author: @misschalupabish2212
text: I just watched this movie yesterday and I was SUPER pumped to see it but then I left the movie theater feeling quite disappointed. I feel the idea for this movie was there but the execution was definitely not‚Ä¶ it had its few quirky moments but that was it. I feel there was a lot of waisted potential to expand on a lot of the ideas they had and to also add backstories scenes to many of the characters. I think this movie would‚Äôve been great if there was more commotion /problem added to the conflict making the resolution just even more dramatic and heartfelt for the two main characters . In the movie one of the guys that Lisa helped kill (Doug) whom they later found out his dad I believe was a detective , and would later get involved in the case of his sons‚Äôs sudden disappearance. I feel the movie could‚Äôve been better if they went more in depth with that and with the drama and commotion of the police looking for her because she was wanted as a notorious murderer. This movie could‚Äôve included some more flashbacks of her mom. Just overall this movie needed more in depth details. It was kinda dry to watch and not a lot of juicy events occurred,that viewers usually crave for. I also wished there was more romance scenes between the two main characters but oh well. Despite all this, the movie had some funny moments and cute scenes. I would not watch again or recommend but still cute.
